Rocco once dated Kim Turnbull. Currently,
he is said to be in a relationship with singer

00:07:59.580 --> 00:08:01.820
Chantelle Lee.

00:08:01.820 --> 00:08:06.699
David Banda.
David was born in 2005, in the southeastern

00:08:06.699 --> 00:08:13.310
African country, Malawi. His biological father,
Yohane, abandoned the newborn in the nursing

00:08:13.310 --> 00:08:18.940
home after his mother died. Later, the baby
was handed over to the 'Home of Hope' orphanage

00:08:18.940 --> 00:08:24.590
located in the district of 'Mchinji.'
A month later, when Madonna visited the orphanage

00:08:24.590 --> 00:08:30.259
while touring for one of her charity programs,
she saw David for the first time. He was not

00:08:30.259 --> 00:08:34.740
in a good health. Suffering from pneumonia
then, the little David was on the verge of

00:08:34.740 --> 00:08:41.449
death. Madonna immediately filed for an adoption
and wanted the baby as soon as possible. After

00:08:41.449 --> 00:08:47.190
the initial official legalities were over,
the baby was finally handed over to Madonna.

00:08:47.190 --> 00:08:52.819
She named the baby David Banda Mwale Ciccone
Ritchie, which included the names of his birthplace

00:08:52.819 --> 00:08:58.629
and Madonna’s then-husband, Guy Ritchie.
Even after Madonna got the permission to adopt

00:08:58.629 --> 00:09:03.689
David, she had to sweat really hard to get
the possession of the baby. At the time of

00:09:03.689 --> 00:09:08.899
David’s adoption, Maddona’s divorce was
already filed. She was battling for the custody

00:09:08.899 --> 00:09:14.800
of her biological son with Guy Ritchie. Out
of nowhere, Yohane came into the picture and

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:19.240
said that he would withdraw the custody as
Madonna's controversial lifestyle might affect

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:26.160
David's future. He wanted the celebrity singer
to first resolve her other legal issues. Madonna

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:31.129
again had to go through all the procedures
for adoption. The legalities ran for a little

00:09:31.129 --> 00:09:36.429
longer. Madonna later visited Malawi, along
with David, to have a final settlement with

00:09:36.429 --> 00:09:42.249
Yohane. That was David’s first visit to
his birthplace after his adoption.

00:09:42.249 --> 00:09:47.490
David was passionate about football from the
very beginning. He started his training early.

00:09:47.490 --> 00:09:52.470
He later moved to Lisbon to continue with
his training under the 'Benfica Academy.'

00:09:52.470 --> 00:09:59.089
In 2018, Madonna visited one of the 'Benfica
Youth' team’s matches to cheer for her son.

00:09:59.089 --> 00:10:04.129
David displayed some incredible skills on
the ground. The Portuguese club, ‘Benfica,’

00:10:04.129 --> 00:10:10.209
won the league and David was even awarded
as the best performer in the 'Under-12' category.

00:10:10.209 --> 00:10:15.439
Madonna and David have made a couple of public
appearances together. The mother-son duo attended

00:10:15.439 --> 00:10:20.660
the 'Rebel Heart Tour' in 2015 where they
were seen singing ‘Like a Prayer.’ They

00:10:20.660 --> 00:10:25.639
also walked on the red carpet of the '2014
Grammy Awards' while donning matching black

00:10:25.639 --> 00:10:31.619
business suits. Madonna, who is highly active
on social media, keeps posting pictures and

00:10:31.619 --> 00:10:37.889
videos featuring David. She once posted a
video footage showing him singing and dancing.

00:10:37.889 --> 00:10:43.149
When Madonna adopted David, she was still
married to Guy Ritchie. This officially makes

00:10:43.149 --> 00:10:45.860
him David’s father.

00:10:45.860 --> 00:10:51.319
Mercy James.
Mercy James was born in 2006 in Malawi. She

00:10:51.319 --> 00:10:57.800
was born to her Malawian parents James Kambewa
and Mwandida Kambewa. Her mother Mwandida

00:10:57.800 --> 00:11:01.459
Kambewa passed away eight days after James'
birth.

00:11:01.459 --> 00:11:03.930
Madonna talked about Mercy in an interview
saying:

00:11:03.930 --> 00:11:09.689
“I met Mercy soon after I met my son David...
Mercy was suffering from malaria, and David

00:11:09.689 --> 00:11:14.140
from pneumonia. And when I held each of them
in my arms, I Whispered in their ears, that

00:11:14.140 --> 00:11:17.850
I would look after them.”
Madonna had to face a lot of troubles while

00:11:17.850 --> 00:11:23.769
adopting James. She discussed it in her speech,
“This time, the judge who was oresiding

00:11:23.769 --> 00:11:28.730
said no. I was recently divorced, and she
informed me, as a divorced woman, I was not

00:11:28.730 --> 00:11:34.059
fit to raise children and that Mercy James
was better of growing up in an orphanage.”

00:11:34.059 --> 00:11:39.179
Madonna fought for over three years to win
the right to adopt Mercy James. Madonna took

00:11:39.179 --> 00:11:45.110
James to her home to start a new life together.
James' original family was heartbroken and

00:11:45.110 --> 00:11:49.949
struggled to give their child away.
James' original family has claimed they have

00:11:49.949 --> 00:11:56.019
no contact with the child since her adoption.
Madonna, however, said Mercy James has never

00:11:56.019 --> 00:12:01.399
been kept away from her culture and heritage.
She is taken to Malawi every year to visit

00:12:01.399 --> 00:12:04.569
her family, friends and to learn about her
roots.

00:12:04.569 --> 00:12:09.589
However, Mercy's parents along with her mother's
best friend are collecting evidence and witnesses

00:12:09.589 --> 00:12:14.689
to go against the adoption and bringing James
back to her original place.

00:12:14.689 --> 00:12:19.310
Mercy James is studying to build her future
career. She might have a net worth around

00:12:19.310 --> 00:12:26.739
$1 million at present, as her mother Madonna
currently shares the net worth of $590 million.

00:12:26.739 --> 00:12:32.100
Mercy James is currently twelve years old
and is too young to get involved in relationships.

00:12:32.100 --> 00:12:37.569
Currently, she is studying and enjoying her
time with Madonna along with her siblings.

00:12:37.569 --> 00:12:42.189
The family is seen spending a vacation to
different destinations, as Madonna shares

00:12:42.189 --> 00:12:47.629
their moments on social networking sites.
In addition, Madonna has opened the country's

00:12:47.629 --> 00:12:53.029
first ever pediatric surgery and intensive
care center, The Mercy James Institution for

00:12:53.029 --> 00:12:56.559
Pediatric Surgery and Intensive Care.

00:12:56.559 --> 00:13:02.939
Twins Stella and Esther.
Twins Stella and Esther were born in 2012.

00:13:02.939 --> 00:13:07.769
Madonna adopted their from Malawi in 2017
after meeting them in an orphanage two years

00:13:07.769 --> 00:13:11.820
earlier.
The pop queen began the adoption process more

00:13:11.820 --> 00:13:16.089
two years ago after being 'compelled' to help
the twins when she saw them at the Home of

00:13:16.089 --> 00:13:19.730
Hope orphanage where they had been left by
their grandmother.

00:13:19.730 --> 00:13:24.819
The actual application was granted in a fortnight,
whereas critics say it normally takes around

00:13:24.819 --> 00:13:29.010
three months.
Speaking about the adoption process, Madonna

00:13:29.010 --> 00:13:33.130
admitted the children are unaware of their
mother's international status after being

00:13:33.130 --> 00:13:39.110
whisked away from a life of poverty in Malawi.
'They don't have a clue and it's a good thing.

00:13:39.110 --> 00:13:44.009
I'm just their mother,' she explained.
The twins' mother died five days after giving

00:13:44.009 --> 00:13:49.170
birth due to complications from a caesarean
section operation in August 2012.

00:13:49.170 --> 00:13:54.540
An initial report by social workers found
their father Adam Mwale had abandoned the

00:13:54.540 --> 00:13:58.820
twins when he walked out on his family after
the death of his wife.

00:13:58.820 --> 00:14:02.439
The girls were left with their grandmother
who did not have the means to care for them

00:14:02.439 --> 00:14:06.740
as well as their five other siblings aged
from eight to 20.

00:14:06.740 --> 00:14:11.499
Stella and Esther have become quite the social
media stars since Madonna adopted them from

00:14:11.499 --> 00:14:17.249
Malawi. She frequently posts pictures of them
in darling outfits and simply just having

00:14:17.249 --> 00:14:29.759
a good time.

